[Black "?"]
[Result "*"]

1.e4 Nf6 2.e5 Nd5 3.d4 c6 {Not a bad move but a bit passive. White can get a comfortable position in many different ways. Here is one suggestion in the spirit of the four pawns attack.} 4.c4 Nc7 5.Nc3 d6 6.f4 g6 7.Be3 Bg7 8.Nf3 O-O 9.Qd2 {White has a small advantage. White has more space and the large center is stable and cannot be challenged easily.}  *

