- allow bxc6 and recapture with the pawn after which the pawn on c6 becomes a target,
- allow bxc6 and recapture with a piece after which the pawn on b7 will be weak,
- take on b5 and if White recaptures with a piece then again b7 will be weak. If White has played a4 as well and recaptures with the a-pawn, then the pawn on a7 will be a target for White.}  *

